cmd-cleandevicelinks-desc = Removes invalid saved device-link references from a map.
cmd-cleandevicelinks-help =
    Usage: {$command} [mapId]
    Removes invalid saved device-link references from the specified map, or from your current map if no map is provided.
cmd-cleandevicelinks-map-missing = Map {$mapId} does not exist.
cmd-cleandevicelinks-cleaned = Cleaned device links on map {$mapId}: removed {$removedSinkEntries} sink references and {$removedLinkPairs} invalid link pairs across {$affectedSources} source entities.
cmd-cleandevicelinks-hint-map = mapId
